# Tesseract OCR language data — was pre-committed as a 5 MB binary cache
# when tesseract.js was used by test scripts that have since been removed.
# Keep this ignore so anyone re-adding tesseract.js doesn't accidentally
# re-commit the blob — it's fetched from the tessdata CDN at runtime.
*.traineddata